name: Deck of Demise - Introduction
description: This NFT is an introduction to the "Deck of Demise" playing card series. The 3D model is composed of scanned images of a physical deck of playing cards to explicitly show the source materials. The "Deck of Demise" series consists of ink drawings and inscriptions on 52 French-suited playing cards. Created summer 2014 at the Resnick Neuropsychiatric Hospital. The drawings and inscriptions exist in addition to the original images. You may contact the creator via their Tezos address.
